parameters: \n<End City Boy>I have to study a lot if I want to become a Diver!
\n<End City Boy>Monsters,\. biomes,\. climate changes...\.\.\. everything stop following the surface's rules in the Hole!
\n<End City Boy>And my big brother got to be down there,\. somewhere...\.\.\. I know it.\.\. It has to be...
"Relics are either long lost artifacts from before the Company settled around the Hole or manifactured artifacts that encapsulate Mana into a serviceable form."
"Taking possession of a Relic is forbidden,\. as the power that lies within it will surely shackle its newfound 'wielder' in a way similiar to what could be described as a curse."
"Monsters that can be found around the Surface include mainly wildlife and small pests intoxicated by the Mana's influence"
"Going alone in caves and holes is unadvisable unless properly armed and trained to battle such creatures."
\n<End City Woman>My son can't get past his brother's disappearance...\.\.\. he's such a sweet kid.
\n<End City Woman>But the Hole shows no mercy.\.\. To anybody.\.\. Now I have to protect the only child I've got left...
